# 7. オーラ

Staff: Move that chair about ten centimeters to your right for me.
Staff: Okay! Is this light good where it is?
Shizuku: (This is it.)
Shizuku: (I've actually left no stone unturned this time around.)
Shizuku: (All that's left is for me to give this shoot everything I have.)
Miku: <Shizuku said that her shoot's today, but where could she be...?>
Miku: <Shizuku, there you...>
Miku: (Oh...)
Miku: (I came to give her some words of encouragement, but I guess that's not going to be necessary.)
Miku: (I believe in you, Shizuku!)
Staff: First, we'll be doing a close-up cut. You're on standby, Hagiyama.
Yu: Understood.
Director: I'm looking forward to seeing a good performance out of you today, Hagiyama.
Yu: Thank you.
Staff: Alright, roll cameras!
Director: And... Action!
Yu: ...
Shizuku: ...!
Shizuku: (Her presence has increased since the audition...!)
Shizuku: (She really is an incredible talent... I mean, her eyes... I'm afraid to even take a breath right now.)
Shizuku: (But...)
Director: Okay! Nice work, Hagiyama. That was a solid take!
Yu: Thank you very much.
Staff: Next, Hinomori, we need you on standby!
Shizuku: Understood...!
Oikawa: Hagiyama's on top of her game today.
Oikawa: All that's left is to see how Hinomori responds.
Shizuku: I'm ready.
Staff: Okay! Looks like everyone else is also ready! Are the cameras ready to roll?!
Film Crew Member: Yes, we're ready!
Shizuku: ...
Shizuku: (This is when everything gets decided.)
Shizuku: (Not just where I'm going to stand in terms of this commercial.)
Shizuku: (But also the future of MORE MORE JUMP!)
Shizuku: (I have to throw everything I have into this moment.)
Shizuku: (I need to use my eyes, lips, fingers and everything else to fully express myself.)
Shizuku: (And carve myself into everyone's memories.)
Shizuku: (This is how overwhelming Shizuku Hinomori's presence can be!)
Yu: ...?!
Shizuku: (I'm nothing like what I was back then.)
Shizuku: (I'm not being made to shoulder my group.)
Shizuku: (We're all working together to share the load as we move forward.)
Shizuku: (But...)
Shizuku: (Right now, I want to carry them all on my back...!)
Shizuku: (I want to carry MORE MORE JUMP! into the future!)
Production Assistant: Okay, roll cameras!
Director: And... Action!
Yu: ...!!
Shizuku: (An aura...)
Shizuku: (I still don't actually know what people mean when they say that.)
Shizuku: (But I believe it's a kind of brilliance that appears when a person's ironclad resolve is supported with an immeasurable amount of hard work.)
Shizuku: (Which means I can shine even brighter now.)
Shizuku: (I'm prepared to carry everyone forward. I worked incredibly hard leading up to this day.)
Shizuku: (So, I will glow brighter than anyone!)
Yu: Oh...
Yu: Wow...
Director: This is...
Oikawa: ...
Oikawa: I wasn't expecting her to shine this brightly...
Director: Is this the Shizuku Hinomori you saw back then, Oikawa?
Oikawa: No.
Oikawa: This goes far beyond what I saw.
Shizuku: Phew...
Shizuku: (I'm so glad that Mr. Oikawa said our commercial is sure to turn out well...)
Shizuku: (I guess that means I did a good job.)
Yu: Nice work today, Hinomori.
Shizuku: Oh, Hagiyama, you as well.
Yu: You were really spectacular today, Hinomori.
Yu: I couldn't take my eyes off of you. The way you used your body was so beautiful...
Yu: And your presence... I was totally overwhelmed.
Yu: I still have a lot of work left to do.
Shizuku: No, I'm the one who still has a lot of work left to do.
Shizuku: Between my current skill level and attitude, I have a long way to go.
Shizuku: You made me realize that, and helped me to improve myself.
Shizuku: So, thank you. I'm glad that I was able to work on this commercial with you, Hagiyama.
Yu: Hinomori...
Yu: Me too. I'm glad it was you I got to work with.
Yu: To tell you the truth, you surprised me a little during the audition...
Yu: It's just... The current you seemed completely different from Shizuku Hinomori from Cheerful * Days.
Yu: But you made me rethink all of that today.
Yu: You're still the Shizuku Hinomori I remember. You're the lead who took Cheerful * Days to the next level.
Shizuku: Oh...
Yu: But...
Yu: Nevermind. I look forward to working with you again.
Shizuku: Me too...!
Yu: (But I'm not losing next time.)
